{"tid":1797240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［被捕手足親屬/朋友必睇］","createTime":"2019-12-25T09:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T15:29:25.000Z","uid":202134,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2832ae189eff95726fa40fa381dcd1942a1ec69","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"小弟細佬比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n朝早<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三點打黎吹父母</span></span>立刻去狗屋簽文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吹完又吹</span></span> 要我哋即刻到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係咁問我地幾點到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本吾比時間我哋搵律師，直到之後我哋堅持要搵律師先去狗屋<br />\n<br />\n班狗竟然<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唉左一聲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n然後佢哋就話收到消息 我老豆去到狗屋 叫我地依家過嚟<br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">我老豆係屋企</span>）<br />\n<br />\n我唔知班狗想做啲乜嘢 極有可能 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想我哋係冇律師嘅情況下處理晒所有嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後佢哋又改口話收到消息我老竇準備出發過去狗屋</span><br />\n<br />\n事後打電話比我老豆 先知 <span style=\"color: red;\">班狗話比我老竇聽我同我阿媽已經到咗狗屋</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n企圖想逼我地所有人到狗屋處理晒所有嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]喺呢一度我只係想同大家講，就算有任何朋友或者親人比狗咬，[size=6]一定要搵律師先 好接佢，你唔會知班狗想點樣搞死我哋</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F127614&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=55019df5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/127614</a><br />\n<br />\n有啲咩唔明嘅就睇呢度啦，啱啱已經見到有家長喺狗屋亂咁講嘢 真心唔好害死自己小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b357adb63d1f260a7922bd2dd4f6f3553e66c28f","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"49760ad0f94221fb77c9125448937fab44da71b6","tid":1797240,"uid":36001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:15:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d633d40d2788c0aeab5fb61fcc891e5e7ab072d","tid":1797240,"uid":150739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e39c7574eaf87bf3a4423beb28f1a6bb1fbdfe8","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f51f74bd890720bc0b4aa4987bf863a83afebb","tid":1797240,"uid":220723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fb1efa4c5090a4e7a95c29ed42ea79701849de5","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a117fdc152f418a1f535964db974605cc90ef8","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f18d844ea944962e2e1224918a45de98ef6d328","tid":1797240,"uid":202142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2832ae189eff95726fa40fa381dcd1942a1ec69","tid":1797240,"uid":202134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"小弟細佬比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n朝早<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三點打黎吹父母</span></span>立刻去狗屋簽文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span